{
  "video_id": "ORthzIOEf30",
  "title": "The biology of our best and worst selves | Robert Sapolsky",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 15276.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: So Robert spent the last few years"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15300.0,
      "end_time": 17636.0,
      "text": "think about how weird human behavior is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17660.0,
      "end_time": 21876.0,
      "text": "and how inadequate most of our language trying to explain it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21900.0,
      "end_time": 26276.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s very exciting to hear him explain some of the thinking behind it"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26300.0,
      "end_time": 27956.0,
      "text": "in public for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27980.0,
      "end_time": 30760.0,
      "text": "Over to you now, Robert Sapolsky."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30100.0,
      "end_time": 33600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34860.0,
      "end_time": 36476.0,
      "text": "Robert Sapolsky: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36500.0,
      "end_time": 38980.0,
      "text": "The fantasy always runs something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39780.0,
      "end_time": 41956.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve overpowered his elite guard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41980.0,
      "end_time": 43915.0,
      "text": "burst into his secret bunker"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43939.0,
      "end_time": 45756.0,
      "text": "with my machine gun ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45780.0,
      "end_time": 47676.0,
      "text": "He lunges for his Luger."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47700.0,
      "end_time": 49516.0,
      "text": "I knock it out of his hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49540.0,
      "end_time": 51876.0,
      "text": "He lunges for his cyanide pill."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51900.0,
      "end_time": 53635.0,
      "text": "I knock that out of his hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53660.0,
      "end_time": 54955.0,
      "text": "He snarls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54980.0,
      "end_time": 57196.0,
      "text": "comes at me with otherworldly strength."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57220.0,
      "end_time": 58916.0,
      "text": "We grapple, we fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58940.0,
      "end_time": 60836.0,
      "text": "I manage to pin him down"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60860.0,
      "end_time": 62420.0,
      "text": "and put on handcuffs."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63300.0,
      "end_time": 65316.0,
      "text": "\"Adolf Hitler,\" I say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65340.0,
      "end_time": 68180.0,
      "text": "\"I arrest you for crimes against humanity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69820.0,
      "end_time": 72795.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s where the Medal of Honor version of the fantasy ends"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72820.0,
      "end_time": 74675.0,
      "text": "and the imagery darkens."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74700.0,
      "end_time": 76419.0,
      "text": "What would I do if I had Hitler?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76980.0,
      "end_time": 79740.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not hard to imagine once I allow myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80540.0,
      "end_time": 82676.0,
      "text": "Sever his spine at the neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82700.0,
      "end_time": 85760.0,
      "text": "Take out his eyes with a blunt instrument."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85100.0,
      "end_time": 87875.0,
      "text": "Puncture his eardrums. Cut out his tongue."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87900.0,
      "end_time": 90360.0,
      "text": "Leave him alive on a respirator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90600.0,
      "end_time": 95356.0,
      "text": "tube-fed, not able to speak or move or see or hear, just to feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95380.0,
      "end_time": 98636.0,
      "text": "and then inject him with something cancerous"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98660.0,
      "end_time": 100916.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s going to fester and pustulate"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100940.0,
      "end_time": 104876.0,
      "text": "until every cell in his body is screaming in agony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104900.0,
      "end_time": 108140.0,
      "text": "until every second feels like an eternity in hell."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109500.0,
      "end_time": 111340.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I would do to Hitler."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113740.0,
      "end_time": 115756.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had this fantasy since I was a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115780.0,
      "end_time": 117276.0,
      "text": "still do sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117300.0,
      "end_time": 119956.0,
      "text": "and when I do, my heart speeds up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119980.0,
      "end_time": 124860.0,
      "text": "all these plans for the most evil, wicked soul in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125660.0,
      "end_time": 126916.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126940.0,
      "end_time": 129835.0,
      "text": "which is I don&#39;t actually believe in souls or evil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129860.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132396.0,
      "text": "and I think wicked belongs in a musical."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132420.0,
      "end_time": 134835.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s some people I would like to see killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134860.0,
      "end_time": 136676.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m against the death penalty."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136700.0,
      "end_time": 138796.0,
      "text": "But I like schlocky violent movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138820.0,
      "end_time": 140596.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m for strict gun control."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140620.0,
      "end_time": 143676.0,
      "text": "But then there was a time I was at a laser tag place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143700.0,
      "end_time": 147579.0,
      "text": "and I had such a good time hiding in a corner shooting at people."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148180.0,
      "end_time": 152980.0,
      "text": "In other words, I&#39;m your basic confused human when it comes to violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153580.0,
      "end_time": 156916.0,
      "text": "Now, as a species, we obviously have problems with violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156940.0,
      "end_time": 159996.0,
      "text": "We use shower heads to deliver poison gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160200.0,
      "end_time": 163116.0,
      "text": "letters with anthrax, airplanes as weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163140.0,
      "end_time": 164995.0,
      "text": "mass rape as a military strategy."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165200.0,
      "end_time": 167300.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re a miserably violent species."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167740.0,
      "end_time": 169236.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a complication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171636.0,
      "text": "which is we don&#39;t hate violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 171660.0,
      "end_time": 173516.0,
      "text": "we hate the wrong kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173540.0,
      "end_time": 174995.0,
      "text": "And when it&#39;s the right kind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175200.0,
      "end_time": 177516.0,
      "text": "we cheer it on, we hand out medals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 177540.0,
      "end_time": 180676.0,
      "text": "we vote for, we mate with our champions of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 180700.0,
      "end_time": 182516.0,
      "text": "When it&#39;s the right kind of violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 182540.0,
      "end_time": 183739.0,
      "text": "we love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 184340.0,
      "end_time": 185996.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s another complication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186200.0,
      "end_time": 190760.0,
      "text": "which is, in addition to us being this miserably violent species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 190100.0,
      "end_time": 193900.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re also this extraordinarily altruistic, compassionate one."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195340.0,
      "end_time": 198636.0,
      "text": "So how do you make sense of the biology of our best behaviors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198660.0,
      "end_time": 202676.0,
      "text": "our worst ones and all of those ambiguously in between?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 202700.0,
      "end_time": 203956.0,
      "text": "Now, for starters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203980.0,
      "end_time": 208275.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s totally boring is understanding the motoric aspects of the behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208300.0,
      "end_time": 211476.0,
      "text": "Your brain tells your spine, tells your muscles"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 211500.0,
      "end_time": 212756.0,
      "text": "to do something or other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 212780.0,
      "end_time": 214716.0,
      "text": "and hooray, you&#39;ve behaved."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214740.0,
      "end_time": 218396.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s hard is understanding the meaning of the behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 218420.0,
      "end_time": 222236.0,
      "text": "because in some settings, pulling a trigger is an appalling act;"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 225236.0,
      "text": "in others, it&#39;s heroically self-sacrificial."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 228196.0,
      "text": "In some settings, putting your hand one someone else&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228220.0,
      "end_time": 229676.0,
      "text": "is deeply compassionate."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 229700.0,
      "end_time": 231595.0,
      "text": "In others, it&#39;s a deep betrayal."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231620.0,
      "end_time": 233156.0,
      "text": "The challenge is to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 233180.0,
      "end_time": 236436.0,
      "text": "the biology of the context of our behaviors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236460.0,
      "end_time": 238600.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s real tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 238860.0,
      "end_time": 242360.0,
      "text": "One thing that&#39;s clear, though, is you&#39;re not going to get anywhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 242600.0,
      "end_time": 246476.0,
      "text": "if you think there&#39;s going to be the brain region or the hormone"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246500.0,
      "end_time": 249236.0,
      "text": "or the gene or the childhood experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252340.0,
      "text": "or the evolutionary mechanism that explains everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252860.0,
      "end_time": 257980.0,
      "text": "Instead, every bit of behavior has multiple levels of causality."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 258620.0,
      "end_time": 260190.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 260660.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261860.00000000003,
      "text": "You have a gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262540.0,
      "end_time": 264116.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a crisis going on:"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264140.0,
      "end_time": 266716.0,
      "text": "rioting, violence, people running around."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 266740.0,
      "end_time": 269916.0,
      "text": "A stranger is running at you in an agitated state --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 269940.0,
      "end_time": 275360.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t quite tell if the expression is frightened, threatening, angry --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275600.0,
      "end_time": 278276.0,
      "text": "holding something that kind of looks like a handgun."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 278300.0,
      "end_time": 279516.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 279540.0,
      "end_time": 281436.0,
      "text": "The stranger comes running at you"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 281460.0,
      "end_time": 283195.0,
      "text": "and you pull the trigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 283220.0,
      "end_time": 286156.0,
      "text": "And it turns out that thing in this person&#39;s hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 286180.0,
      "end_time": 287380.0,
      "text": "was a cell phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 288200.0,
      "end_time": 290236.0,
      "text": "So we asked this biological question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 293436.0,
      "text": "what was going on that caused this behavior?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 293460.0,
      "end_time": 295356.0,
      "text": "What caused this behavior?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 295380.0,
      "end_time": 297676.0,
      "text": "And this is a multitude of questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 297700.0,
      "end_time": 298916.0,
      "text": "We start."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 298940.0,
      "end_time": 303356.0,
      "text": "What was going on in your brain one second before you pulled that trigger?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 303380.0,
      "end_time": 307760.0,
      "text": "And this brings us into the realm of a brain region called the amygdala."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 307100.0,
      "end_time": 311360.0,
      "text": "The amygdala, which is central to violence, central to fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 311600.0,
      "end_time": 313756.0,
      "text": "initiates volleys of cascades"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 313780.0,
      "end_time": 316350.0,
      "text": "that produce pulling of a trigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 316600.0,
      "end_time": 319740.0,
      "text": "What was the level of activity in your amygdala one second before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 320700.0,
      "end_time": 324750.0,
      "text": "But to understand that, we have to step back a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 324100.0,
      "end_time": 327676.0,
      "text": "What was going on in the environment seconds to minutes before"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 327700.0,
      "end_time": 329436.0,
      "text": "that impacted the amygdala?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 329460.0,
      "end_time": 332556.0,
      "text": "Now, obviously, the sights, the sounds of the rioting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 332580.0,
      "end_time": 333796.0,
      "text": "that was pertinent."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 333820.0,
      "end_time": 335360.0,
      "text": "But in addition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 335600.0,
      "end_time": 338516.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re more likely to mistake a cell phone for a handgun"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 338540.0,
      "end_time": 340796.0,
      "text": "if that stranger was male"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 340820.0,
      "end_time": 343420.0,
      "text": "and large and of a different race."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 344180.0,
      "end_time": 346316.0,
      "text": "Furthermore, if you&#39;re in pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 346340.0,
      "end_time": 348515.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re hungry, if you&#39;re exhausted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 348540.0,
      "end_time": 351760.0,
      "text": "your frontal cortex is not going to work as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 351100.0,
      "end_time": 354756.0,
      "text": "part of the brain whose job it is to get to the amygdala in time"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 354780.0,
      "end_time": 358590.0,
      "text": "saying, \"Are you really sure that&#39;s a gun there?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 358620.0,
      "end_time": 360756.0,
      "text": "But we need to step further back."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 360780.0,
      "end_time": 363955.0,
      "text": "Now we have to look at hours to days before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 363980.0,
      "end_time": 366956.0,
      "text": "and with this, we have entered the realm of hormones."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 366980.0,
      "end_time": 369116.0,
      "text": "For example, testosterone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 369140.0,
      "end_time": 370876.0,
      "text": "where regardless of your sex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 370900.0,
      "end_time": 373756.0,
      "text": "if you have elevated testosterone levels in your blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 373780.0,
      "end_time": 377155.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re more likely to think a face with a neutral expression"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 377180.0,
      "end_time": 379236.0,
      "text": "is instead looking threatening."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 383116.0,
      "text": "Elevated testosterone levels, elevated levels of stress hormones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 383140.0,
      "end_time": 385436.0,
      "text": "and your amygdala is going to be more active"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 385460.0,
      "end_time": 387940.0,
      "text": "and your frontal cortex will be more sluggish."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 389200.0,
      "end_time": 391876.0,
      "text": "Pushing back further, weeks to months before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 391900.0,
      "end_time": 393356.0,
      "text": "where&#39;s the relevance there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 393380.0,
      "end_time": 395916.0,
      "text": "This is the realm of neural plasticity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 395940.0,
      "end_time": 399876.0,
      "text": "the fact that your brain can change in response to experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 399900.0,
      "end_time": 404750.0,
      "text": "and if your previous months have been filled with stress and trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 404100.0,
      "end_time": 405956.0,
      "text": "your amygdala will have enlarged."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 405980.0,
      "end_time": 408196.0,
      "text": "The neurons will have become more excitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 408220.0,
      "end_time": 410556.0,
      "text": "your frontal cortex would have atrophied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 410580.0,
      "end_time": 413380.0,
      "text": "all relevant to what happens in that one second."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 414140.0,
      "end_time": 416796.0,
      "text": "But we push back even more, back years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 416820.0,
      "end_time": 419316.0,
      "text": "back, for example, to your adolescence."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 419340.0,
      "end_time": 421835.0,
      "text": "Now, the central fact of the adolescent brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 421860.0,
      "end_time": 424596.0,
      "text": "is all of it is going full blast"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 424620.0,
      "end_time": 426316.0,
      "text": "except the frontal cortex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 426340.0,
      "end_time": 428750.0,
      "text": "which is still half-baked."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 428100.0,
      "end_time": 431276.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t fully mature until you&#39;re around 25."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 431300.0,
      "end_time": 434516.0,
      "text": "And thus, adolescence and early adulthood"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 434540.0,
      "end_time": 439676.0,
      "text": "are the years where environment and experience sculpt your frontal cortex"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 439700.0,
      "end_time": 443500.0,
      "text": "into the version you&#39;re going to have as an adult in that critical moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 444620.0,
      "end_time": 446396.0,
      "text": "But pushing back even further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 446420.0,
      "end_time": 449876.0,
      "text": "even further back to childhood and fetal life"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 449900.0,
      "end_time": 452715.0,
      "text": "and all the different versions that that could come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 452740.0,
      "end_time": 455996.0,
      "text": "Now, obviously, that&#39;s the time that your brain is being constructed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 456200.0,
      "end_time": 457236.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 460556.0,
      "text": "but in addition, experience during those times"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 460580.0,
      "end_time": 463556.0,
      "text": "produce what are called epigenetic changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 463580.0,
      "end_time": 465236.0,
      "text": "permanent, in some cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 469596.0,
      "text": "permanently activating certain genes, turning off others."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 469620.0,
      "end_time": 471116.0,
      "text": "And as an example of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 471140.0,
      "end_time": 476156.0,
      "text": "if as a fetus you were exposed to a lot of stress hormones through your mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 476180.0,
      "end_time": 479596.0,
      "text": "epigenetics is going to produce your amygdala in adulthood"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 479620.0,
      "end_time": 481556.0,
      "text": "as a more excitable form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 481580.0,
      "end_time": 484219.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re going to have elevated stress hormone levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 484780.0,
      "end_time": 486676.0,
      "text": "But pushing even further back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 486700.0,
      "end_time": 488396.0,
      "text": "back to when you were just a fetus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 488420.0,
      "end_time": 491236.0,
      "text": "back to when all you were was a collection of genes."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 493635.0,
      "text": "Now, genes are really important to all of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 493660.0,
      "end_time": 496396.0,
      "text": "but critically, genes don&#39;t determine anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 496420.0,
      "end_time": 500600.0,
      "text": "because genes work differently in different environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 500460.0,
      "end_time": 501715.0,
      "text": "Key example here:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 501740.0,
      "end_time": 504876.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a variant of a gene called MAO-A,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 504900.0,
      "end_time": 506556.0,
      "text": "and if you have that variant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 506580.0,
      "end_time": 511236.0,
      "text": "you are far more likely to commit antisocial violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 515236.0,
      "text": "if, and only if, you were abused as a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517635.0,
      "text": "Genes and environment interact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 517659.0,
      "end_time": 521275.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s happening in that one second before you pull that trigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 521299.0,
      "end_time": 525540.0,
      "text": "reflects your lifetime of those gene-environment interactions."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 526499.0,
      "end_time": 530116.0,
      "text": "Now, remarkably enough, we&#39;ve got to push even further back now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 530140.0,
      "end_time": 531516.0,
      "text": "back centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 531540.0,
      "end_time": 533876.0,
      "text": "What were your ancestors up to."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 533900.0,
      "end_time": 537760.0,
      "text": "And if, for example, they were nomadic pastoralists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 537100.0,
      "end_time": 538356.0,
      "text": "they were pastoralists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 538380.0,
      "end_time": 540956.0,
      "text": "people living in deserts or grasslands"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 540980.0,
      "end_time": 543636.0,
      "text": "with their herds of camels, cows, goats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 543660.0,
      "end_time": 547716.0,
      "text": "odds are they would have invented what&#39;s called a culture of honor"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 547740.0,
      "end_time": 549956.0,
      "text": "filled with warrior classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 549980.0,
      "end_time": 552676.0,
      "text": "retributive violence, clan vendettas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 552700.0,
      "end_time": 554956.0,
      "text": "and amazingly, centuries later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 554980.0,
      "end_time": 558660.0,
      "text": "that would still be influencing the values with which you were raised."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 559620.0,
      "end_time": 561756.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ve got to push even further back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 561780.0,
      "end_time": 563516.0,
      "text": "back millions of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 563540.0,
      "end_time": 565596.0,
      "text": "because if we&#39;re talking about genes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 565620.0,
      "end_time": 569276.0,
      "text": "implicitly we&#39;re now talking about the evolution of genes."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 569300.0,
      "end_time": 571516.0,
      "text": "And what you see is, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 571540.0,
      "end_time": 574360.0,
      "text": "patterns across different primate species."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 574600.0,
      "end_time": 578476.0,
      "text": "Some of them have evolved for extremely low levels of aggression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 578500.0,
      "end_time": 581360.0,
      "text": "others have evolved in the opposite direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 581600.0,
      "end_time": 584955.0,
      "text": "and floating there in between by every measure are humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 584980.0,
      "end_time": 588876.0,
      "text": "once again this confused, barely defined species"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 588900.0,
      "end_time": 592140.0,
      "text": "that has all these potentials to go one way or the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 593380.0,
      "end_time": 595196.0,
      "text": "So what has this gotten us to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 595220.0,
      "end_time": 597196.0,
      "text": "Basically, what we&#39;re seeing here is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 597220.0,
      "end_time": 599116.0,
      "text": "if you want to understand a behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 599140.0,
      "end_time": 601996.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s an appalling one, a wondrous one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 602200.0,
      "end_time": 603756.0,
      "text": "or confusedly in between,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 603780.0,
      "end_time": 605315.0,
      "text": "if you want to understand that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 605340.0,
      "end_time": 608796.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got take into account what happened a second before"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 608820.0,
      "end_time": 610276.0,
      "text": "to a million years before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 610300.0,
      "end_time": 611955.0,
      "text": "everything in between."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 611980.0,
      "end_time": 613956.0,
      "text": "So what can we conclude at this point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 613980.0,
      "end_time": 616276.0,
      "text": "Officially, it&#39;s complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 616300.0,
      "end_time": 617915.0,
      "text": "Wow, that&#39;s really helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 617940.0,
      "end_time": 619196.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 619220.0,
      "end_time": 622796.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;d better be real careful, real cautious"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 622820.0,
      "end_time": 626156.0,
      "text": "before you conclude you know what causes a behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 626180.0,
      "end_time": 628939.0,
      "text": "especially if it&#39;s a behavior you&#39;re judging harshly."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 630420.0,
      "end_time": 634396.0,
      "text": "Now, to me, the single most important point about all of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 634420.0,
      "end_time": 636795.0,
      "text": "is one having to do with change."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 636820.0,
      "end_time": 643196.0,
      "text": "Every bit of biology I have mentioned here can change in different circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 643220.0,
      "end_time": 646360.0,
      "text": "For example, ecosystems change."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 646600.0,
      "end_time": 650476.0,
      "text": "Thousands of years ago, the Sahara was a lush grassland."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 650500.0,
      "end_time": 652116.0,
      "text": "Cultures change."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 652140.0,
      "end_time": 656476.0,
      "text": "In the 17th century, the most terrifying people in Europe were the Swedes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 656500.0,
      "end_time": 658236.0,
      "text": "rampaging all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 658260.0,
      "end_time": 660436.0,
      "text": "This is what the Swedish military does now."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 660460.0,
      "end_time": 662300.0,
      "text": "They haven&#39;t had a war in 200 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 663100.0,
      "end_time": 664556.0,
      "text": "Most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 664580.0,
      "end_time": 666196.0,
      "text": "brains change."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 666220.0,
      "end_time": 668236.0,
      "text": "Neurons grow new processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 669716.0,
      "text": "Circuits disconnect."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 669740.0,
      "end_time": 671396.0,
      "text": "Everything in the brain changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 671420.0,
      "end_time": 676620.0,
      "text": "and out of this come extraordinary examples of human change."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 677220.0,
      "end_time": 678836.0,
      "text": "First one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 678860.0,
      "end_time": 680556.0,
      "text": "this is a man named John Newton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 680580.0,
      "end_time": 681916.0,
      "text": "a British theologian"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 681940.0,
      "end_time": 686676.0,
      "text": "who played a central role in the abolition of slavery from the British Empire"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 686700.0,
      "end_time": 688716.0,
      "text": "in the early 1800s."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 688740.0,
      "end_time": 693476.0,
      "text": "And amazingly, this man spent decades as a younger man"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 693500.0,
      "end_time": 695636.0,
      "text": "as the captain of a slave ship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 695660.0,
      "end_time": 698596.0,
      "text": "and then as an investor in slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 698620.0,
      "end_time": 700756.0,
      "text": "growing rich from this."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 700780.0,
      "end_time": 703435.0,
      "text": "And then something changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 703460.0,
      "end_time": 704996.0,
      "text": "Something changed in him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 705200.0,
      "end_time": 710276.0,
      "text": "something that Newton himself celebrated in the thing that he&#39;s most famous for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 710300.0,
      "end_time": 711915.0,
      "text": "a hymn that he wrote:"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 711940.0,
      "end_time": 713340.0,
      "text": "\"Amazing Grace.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 714860.0,
      "end_time": 719756.0,
      "text": "This is a man named Zenji Abe on the morning of December 6, 1941,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 719780.0,
      "end_time": 724756.0,
      "text": "about to lead a squadron of Japanese bombers to attack Pearl Harbor."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 724780.0,
      "end_time": 728315.0,
      "text": "And this is the same man 50 years later to the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 728340.0,
      "end_time": 731916.0,
      "text": "hugging a man who survived the attack on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 731940.0,
      "end_time": 733356.0,
      "text": "And as an old man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 733380.0,
      "end_time": 737796.0,
      "text": "Zenji Abe came to a collection of Pearl Harbor survivors"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 737820.0,
      "end_time": 739236.0,
      "text": "at a ceremony there"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 739260.0,
      "end_time": 743580.0,
      "text": "and in halting English apologized for what he had done as a young man."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 744580.0,
      "end_time": 746476.0,
      "text": "Now, it doesn&#39;t always require decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 746500.0,
      "end_time": 750196.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, extraordinary change could happen in just hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 750220.0,
      "end_time": 754596.0,
      "text": "Consider the World War I Christmas truce of 1914."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 754620.0,
      "end_time": 757756.0,
      "text": "The powers that be had negotiated a brief truce"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 757780.0,
      "end_time": 759396.0,
      "text": "so that soldiers could go out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 759420.0,
      "end_time": 763315.0,
      "text": "collect bodies from no-man&#39;s-land in between the trench lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 763340.0,
      "end_time": 766276.0,
      "text": "And soon British and German soldiers"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 766300.0,
      "end_time": 767756.0,
      "text": "were doing that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 767780.0,
      "end_time": 770236.0,
      "text": "and then helping each other carry bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 770260.0,
      "end_time": 773915.0,
      "text": "and then helping each other dig graves in the frozen ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 773940.0,
      "end_time": 775196.0,
      "text": "and then praying together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 775220.0,
      "end_time": 778360.0,
      "text": "and then having Christmas together and exchanging gifts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 778600.0,
      "end_time": 781276.0,
      "text": "and by the next day, they were playing soccer together"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 781300.0,
      "end_time": 784675.0,
      "text": "and exchanging addresses so they could meet after the war."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 784700.0,
      "end_time": 788676.0,
      "text": "That truce kept going until the officers had to arrive"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 788700.0,
      "end_time": 790196.0,
      "text": "and said, \"We will shoot you"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 790220.0,
      "end_time": 792716.0,
      "text": "unless you go back to trying to kill each other.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 792740.0,
      "end_time": 794876.0,
      "text": "And all it took here was hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 794900.0,
      "end_time": 799236.0,
      "text": "for these men to develop a completely new category of \"us,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 799260.0,
      "end_time": 801156.0,
      "text": "all of us in the trenches here"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 801180.0,
      "end_time": 803955.0,
      "text": "on both sides, dying for no damn reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 803980.0,
      "end_time": 807636.0,
      "text": "and who is a \"them,\" those faceless powers behind the lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 807660.0,
      "end_time": 809260.0,
      "text": "who were using them as pawns."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 810500.0,
      "end_time": 813700.0,
      "text": "And sometimes, change can occur in seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 814540.0,
      "end_time": 817876.0,
      "text": "Probably the most horrifying event in the Vietnam War"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 817900.0,
      "end_time": 819795.0,
      "text": "was the My Lai Massacre."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 819820.0,
      "end_time": 821836.0,
      "text": "A brigade of American soldiers"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 821860.0,
      "end_time": 824876.0,
      "text": "went into an undefended village full of civilians"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 824900.0,
      "end_time": 828435.0,
      "text": "and killed between 350 and 500 of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 828460.0,
      "end_time": 831316.0,
      "text": "mass-raped women and children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 831340.0,
      "end_time": 832916.0,
      "text": "mutilated bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 832940.0,
      "end_time": 834156.0,
      "text": "It was appalling."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 834180.0,
      "end_time": 838435.0,
      "text": "It was appalling because it occurred, because the government denied it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 838460.0,
      "end_time": 842836.0,
      "text": "because the US government eventually did nothing more than a slap on the wrist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 842860.0,
      "end_time": 847116.0,
      "text": "and appalling because it almost certainly was not a singular event."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 847140.0,
      "end_time": 852236.0,
      "text": "This man, Hugh Thompson, this is the man who stopped the My Lai Massacre."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 852260.0,
      "end_time": 854876.0,
      "text": "He was piloting a helicopter gunship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 854900.0,
      "end_time": 856716.0,
      "text": "landed there, got out"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 856740.0,
      "end_time": 859796.0,
      "text": "and saw American soldiers shooting babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 859820.0,
      "end_time": 861196.0,
      "text": "shooting old women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 861220.0,
      "end_time": 863116.0,
      "text": "figured out what was going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 863140.0,
      "end_time": 865236.0,
      "text": "and he then took his helicopter"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 865260.0,
      "end_time": 869236.0,
      "text": "and did something that undid his lifetime of conditioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 869260.0,
      "end_time": 871316.0,
      "text": "as to who is an \"us\" and who is a \"them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 871340.0,
      "end_time": 873196.0,
      "text": "He landed his helicopter"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 873220.0,
      "end_time": 876836.0,
      "text": "in between some surviving villagers and American soldiers"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 876860.0,
      "end_time": 880516.0,
      "text": "and he trained his machine guns on his fellow Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 880540.0,
      "end_time": 884420.0,
      "text": "and said, \"If you don&#39;t stop the killing, I will mow you down.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 886380.0,
      "end_time": 889356.0,
      "text": "Now, these people are no more special than any of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 889380.0,
      "end_time": 891956.0,
      "text": "Same neurons, same neurochemicals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 891980.0,
      "end_time": 893300.0,
      "text": "same biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 894220.0,
      "end_time": 897596.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re left with here is this inevitable cliche:"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 897620.0,
      "end_time": 900356.0,
      "text": "\"Those who don&#39;t study history are destined to repeat it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 900380.0,
      "end_time": 902556.0,
      "text": "What we have here is the opposite of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 902580.0,
      "end_time": 906836.0,
      "text": "Those who don&#39;t study the history of extraordinary human change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 906860.0,
      "end_time": 910396.0,
      "text": "those who don&#39;t study the biology of what can transform us"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 910420.0,
      "end_time": 912915.0,
      "text": "from our worst to our best behaviors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 912940.0,
      "end_time": 915996.0,
      "text": "those who don&#39;t do this are destined not to be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 916200.0,
      "end_time": 919900.0,
      "text": "to repeat these incandescent, magnificent moments."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 920300.0,
      "end_time": 921500.0,
      "text": "So thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 921860.0,
      "end_time": 925940.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 931860.0,
      "end_time": 935356.0,
      "text": "CA: Talks that really give you a new mental model about something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 935380.0,
      "end_time": 937316.0,
      "text": "those are some of my favorite TED Talks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 937340.0,
      "end_time": 939600.0,
      "text": "and we just got one."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 939780.0,
      "end_time": 942636.0,
      "text": "Robert, thank you so much for that. Good luck with the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 942660.0,
      "end_time": 943915.0,
      "text": "That was amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 943940.0,
      "end_time": 947116.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to try and get you to come here in person one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 947140.0,
      "end_time": 948356.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 948380.0,
      "end_time": 949860.0,
      "text": "RS: Thank you. Thank you all."
    }
  ]
}